Ranger Help for: compare equipment
===================================

SYNTAX:      compare <item1> to <item2>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     5
SKILL TYPE:  assessment

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to compare two pieces of equipment, either
weapons or armor, and determine which is of higher quality. The accuracy
of the comparison depends on the Ranger's guild level. Higher ranked
Rangers can discern finer differences between items. Both items must
be in the Ranger's inventory to be compared.
